casebody.data:
Gregory J. TENCZA; 314 Atlantic Avenue-Spring Lake LLC, Plaintiffs-Respondents,
v.
Edward PETRAGLIA, Defendant. M-1021/1022 September Term 2017
080628 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 24, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the miscellaneous motion of Karen Hurd-Petraglia "to confirm stay of the February 16, 2018 eviction" pending appeal (M-1021) and for other alternative forms of relief, including a stay (M-1022) are denied.

CLERK OF THE SUPREME COURT.
